{"tid":2328804,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"宮脇咲良憔悴暴瘦、臉頰凹陷！「忙到忘記吃了甚麼、何時睡過覺」","createTime":"2020-12-16T19:10:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-17T08:26:29.000Z","uid":152123,"like":9,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"70734ca7215b625f729fdb65046b8ce56d9c6650","tid":2328804,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T19:10:57.000Z","msg":"出道期<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EX478XeWsAErWfB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEX478XeWsAErWfB.jpg&h=69a4d5e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DrDYYavUwAAYK6k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDrDYYavUwAAYK6k.jpg&h=391bc4e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.asiachan.com/Miyawaki.Sakura.full.187554.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.asiachan.com%2FMiyawaki.Sakura.full.187554.jpg&h=d667fd42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/6f/05/55/6f055504bb430c969994f0d3417c61d3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2F6f%2F05%2F55%2F6f055504bb430c969994f0d3417c61d3.jpg&h=7fba0491&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n現在：<br />\n<img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/55bf60e1bff66a34c2ac42ca08c6072c/307416b8d6fa638b-53/s400x600/a48dea204706318df5452a3ba0a731e7c88ee2f9.gifv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F64.media.tumblr.com%2F55bf60e1bff66a34c2ac42ca08c6072c%2F307416b8d6fa638b-53%2Fs400x600%2Fa48dea204706318df5452a3ba0a731e7c88ee2f9.gifv&h=92bd8f6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EpBs0LXUUAE8H06.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEpBs0LXUUAE8H06.jpg&h=e975770f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://instagrammernewsimg.s3.ap-northeast-1-ntt.wasabisys.com/CIzJBXSgThF\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagrammernewsimg.s3.ap-northeast-1-ntt.wasabisys.com%2FCIzJBXSgThF&h=707231b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Znashwo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZnashwo.jpg&h=df993f2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n宮脇咲良個人電台節目 內容節錄：<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-small\">Saku no ki summary<br />\n<br />\nSakura: *hums Panorama* It's already 9 days since comeback? So fast~ <br />\nShe's recording after Inkigayo<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"large\">Sakura: I want people to understand just how hard it is for K-Pop idols during comebacks... I don't think any of us slept that much for the past week. I don't know what I ate, what time it is now, when I last slept...</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nFan was touched by the dance which incorporates earlier choreos &amp; asked if there were any hard parts?<br />\nYoungjun-sensei's choreo is powerful, uses a lot of power. To convey the strength while still maintaining the elegance was the hard part for Sakura.<br />\n<br />\nSakura: We showed off our new song for the first time at MAMA, but we were so nervous! Also, the stage was so humongous! It was in a studio, but the first time I saw it, I was just like, &quot;B-B-Big!&quot; 😲<br />\n<br />\nSakura: It's pretty cool how fans can find meaning in everything. Even for MVs, we're just told what expression to make or what to do at each point, so we know what the actual scene is, but we don't know the story 😂😂<br />\n<br />\nSakura: Then the fans will watch it and say, &quot;Oh, this part obviously means this, or this part refers to so and so...&quot; Then we read it and think, &quot;Oh, that sounds right!&quot; or &quot;Ah, is that it?!&quot; 🤣<br />\n<br />\nSakura: Sequence is a really nice song. I love the dance. Dancing to it is really fun. Rather than following the beat, it's more like you're guided by the beat while dancing. It's fun. Pls check out the fan cam~<br />\n<br />\nSakura about the 'Let's fly together' part: It's not a pair dance with just me &amp; Wonyoung, but Nako &amp; Hiichan were doing their best to form the wings behind Wonyoung too! It's really cute~ (laughs) Pls check out Nako's fancam to see it!<br />\n<br />\nSakura's current fav song is 'O Sole Mio'<br />\n<br />\nSakura: The best way to get something across to Korean members is probably to look up how to write it in Korean. Korean pronunciation is pretty difficult, so rather than say it, it's easier to write it &amp; tell them to look at it 😁<br />\n<br />\nSakura: Plus, if reception problems occur and we can't hear you but you can hear us, that paper with your question written comes in handy</span><br />\n<br />\n求下CJ放過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />反正次次佢同純B都係行行企企得幾秒鏡頭 畀佢去食飯啦"},{"pid":"ca5de1cf5a1de5dda447f4a069f62c9d797ca15e","tid":2328804,"uid":119390,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T19:16:53.000Z","msg":"呢個時期最靚<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HVqctGU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHVqctGU.png&h=dde23681&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e1f2afe0c4ff1046f1f8c989e801a132e8cbc7f0","tid":2328804,"uid":152123,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"ca5de1cf5a1de5dda447f4a069f62c9d797ca15e","tid":2328804,"uid":119390,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T19:16:53.000Z","msg":"呢個時期最靚<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HVqctGU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHVqctGU.png&h=dde23681&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T19:19:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/CgFO5bsUYAAJzZO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FCgFO5bsUYAAJzZO.jpg&h=7d1566b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.alicdn.com/imgextra/i2/20816277/O1CN01Ku1wWO1wEubipXgbX_!!20816277.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i